    "long_instructions": "### Walk-Up Songs\r\n\r\n**Do This:**\r\n1) Let's make your second walk-up song. Refer to your Activity Guide to determine the mood and personality of this character. \r\n2) Add your tracks under `when run`. \r\n  - Your song should be at least 8 measures.\r\n3) When you have a sequence you like, drag the `2 triggered immediately` block to your workspace and move all the code under `when run` to the trigger block.\r\n\r\nPress \"Run\" and then practice pressing \"1\" or \"2\" to trigger each walk up song you've made so far. ",
